text.tspan: Steve Carwell, (BSEE), has spent several decades in various executive positions in the
areospace, medical devices, industrial products and sporting goods industries. His
management experience includes serving as CEO of a publicly traded medical device
manufacturer as well as working for 3 Fortune 500 companies. He eventually founded
Jadestone Consulting where he worked with client companies throughout the U.S. and
abroad. He has a proven track record as CFO, International Business Manager, Direc
tor of Sales & Market Development, and Director of Operations with experience in
Quality Control, Process Engineering, Project Management, ISO Regulatory Compli
ance, OSHA & FDA Compliance, Domestic and International Sales, Organizational
Development, Technical Manufacturing and Lean Six Sigma Implementation.
